title: Simpsons Comics Mega Pack Add On Supplement 1
description:
An addon compiled by me of comics brought out since the mega pack was released.

Some were hard to find and required a lot of searching, most required converting from other formats and needed cropping and alignment.

A couple that I could not find had to be made from kindle screenshots.

Decided to put this on here so other fans don't have to go through the same. 

If you like the comics and can afford to do so, please buy an issue or a few to show your support and so they keep making them.
